dct_description_sm: Relief shown by approximate 50 feet contours interval and spot elevations. Includes a guide to numbered features, street index,diagrams to boundaries and elevation guide. In lower right margin: "This is a photomap base controlled by the best average fit to the 1:125,000 scale topographic map. Features may be displaced particularly in areas of varying terrain heights. Stock no. G961XABEOKUT101; and G961XABEOKUT201
